// Title: Suspicious Event Log Service Stopped
// Description: Detects stopping of the Windows Event Log service which may indicate attempts to disable logging.
// Data Source: SecurityEvent
// MITRE ATT&CK:
//   Tactic: TA0005 - Defense Evasion
//   Technique: T1562.002 - Disable Windows Event Logging
// Severity: High

SecurityEvent
| where EventID == 7036
| where Activity contains "Windows Event Log"
| project TimeGenerated, Computer, Activity
| order by TimeGenerated desc